ActWestern Economic Diversification Act
SubjectAgreements with the Provinces of British Columbia, Alberta, Saskatchewan and Manitoba for the delivery of the Community Adjustment Fund.
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Western Economic Diversification to enter into cost-shared agreements with each of the governments of the provinces of British Columbia, Alberta, Saskatchewan and Manitoba, for the purpose of delivering the Community Adjustment Fund (CAF).
